# Trivy vulnerability ignore list.
#
# Format: one CVE/GHSA ID per line. Lines beginning with '#' are comments.

# github.com/docker/docker is pulled in transitively via testcontainers-go,
# which is a *test-only* dependency. It never ships in the library's runtime
# code path.
#
# Trivy reports these as fixed in Docker Engine v29.3.1, but that release has
# not been published as a Go module (latest proxy.golang.org tag is v28.5.2),
# so there is no version we can bump to. Revisit once docker/docker publishes
# a v29.x Go module tag that incorporates the fix.
CVE-2026-33997
CVE-2026-34040
